{
  "stem": "11611.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His wife, who got this phony annulment, had the kids who grew up and finally went to law school in the United States.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When Werber finished his prison term, which is about six years later at Lewisburg, he went back to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He could never enter the United States again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's always been barred.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He won't be at the reunion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I then traveled one year to Vienna, and I called him up because to hell with all the political background-- it had nothing really to do with me.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was an old friend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he-- he had remarried, he was now married to some German-Austrian woman, who was an interpreter of a communist conferences-- Russian, Czech, whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was staying in a hotel in some outlying section of Vienna, and he said he'd come by and pick us up for dinner.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And his daughter from Virginia, who lived in Virginia, was visiting at the same time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He comes by in a Jaguar convertible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Living it up, I mean, obviously.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He then took us all to dinner in some monastery, which was a very good restaurant, excellent food in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was very lavish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I asked him what the hell he was doing, and I suspect that during these years he was doing the same thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was still being a communist spy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was now an international tax expert, with a background in chemistry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he used to travel all over Europe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I figured that was some kind of official prescribed duty on behalf of his masters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as I know, he is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Have I been in touch with him since?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I haven't really seen him-- maybe the last time was 15 years ago.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I wouldn't hesitate to go see him.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
